25. **vehicle1_c1.frontAxleAssembly has part: frontAxle of type FrontAxle**: Yes (SteerableFrontAxleAssembly has axle : SteerableFrontAxle, which specializes FrontAxle).
26. **vehicle1_c1.frontAxleAssembly has part: frontWheel of type Wheel[2] ordered**: **No** (see above).
